.SH BUGS
The functions
.IR aes_encrypt ,
.IR aes_decrypt ,
.IR aesCTRencrypt ,
.IR aesCTRdecrypt ,
.IR setupAESXCBCstate ,
and
.IR aesXCBCmac
have not yet been verified by running test vectors through them.
